WARNING: Kevin Allison of the groundbreaking sketch comedy troupe The State &amp; the RISK! podcast joins the first timer club on today's Comedy Bing Bong! Kevin lets us know the deets surrounding the upcoming The State reunion at Festival Supreme, the origin of his RISK! podcast, and how he became a faculty member at a Kink camp. Also joining us for the first time is entrepreneur Bridgette Murphy who tells us all about her Irish gift shop "Bridgette's Irish Gifts" &amp; a special gift that Scott received known as HP-DP-69B aka the Hewlett-Packard Sex Robot. Plus, they all become familiar with Riddle Me This!

